{
 "fragments": [
  {
   "begin": "0.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "3.360", 
   "id": "s000001", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Herr Pr\u00e4sident! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "3.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "7.120", 
   "id": "s000002", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sehr geehrte Kolleginnen und Kollegen! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "7.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "7.480", 
   "id": "s000003", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich glaube, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "7.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "8.320", 
   "id": "s000004", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "nicht nur der Bericht, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "8.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "10.480", 
   "id": "s000005", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sondern auch diese Debatte zeigt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "10.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "11.440", 
   "id": "s000006", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass die Religions- "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "11.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "14.840", 
   "id": "s000007", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und Weltanschauungsfreiheit ein wirklich immens hohes Gut ist, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "14.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "17.320", 
   "id": "s000008", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das es immer wieder zu sch\u00fctzen gilt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "17.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "26.520", 
   "id": "s000009", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie ist Teil der UN-Menschenrechtscharta und der Europ\u00e4ischen Menschenrechtskonvention und nat\u00fcrlich auch ein immens wichtiger Bestandteil unserer Au\u00dfen- "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "26.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "28.480", 
   "id": "s000010", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und Sicherheitspolitik. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "28.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "34.040", 
   "id": "s000011", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Einschr\u00e4nkungen dieser Freiheit sind nichts anderes als Menschenrechtsverletzungen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "34.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "35.440", 
   "id": "s000012", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Diese m\u00fcssen benannt und, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "35.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "36.560", 
   "id": "s000013", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wo immer m\u00f6glich, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "36.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "39.160", 
   "id": "s000014", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "nat\u00fcrlich beseitigt werden."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "39.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "43.320", 
   "id": "s000015", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "In dieser Debatte ist deutlich geworden: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "43.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "46.080", 
   "id": "s000016", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Man steht nur dann wirklich glaubw\u00fcrdig f\u00fcr Religions- "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "46.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "48.080", 
   "id": "s000017", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und Weltanschauungsfreiheit, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "48.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "52.600", 
   "id": "s000018", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wenn man Gruppen nicht gegeneinander ausspielt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "52.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "59.640", 
   "id": "s000019", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sondern es damit wirklich f\u00fcr alle ernst meint."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "59.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "63.400", 
   "id": "s000020", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die benannten Konflikte haben leider eines gemeinsam: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "63.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "70.160", 
   "id": "s000021", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es wird selten \u00fcber religi\u00f6se Inhalte debattiert und gestritten. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "70.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "71.640", 
   "id": "s000022", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es geht um Macht, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "71.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "72.960", 
   "id": "s000023", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "es geht um Dominanz,"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "72.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "74.960", 
   "id": "s000024", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "es geht um Unterdr\u00fcckung, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "74.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "75.960", 
   "id": "s000025", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und es geht darum, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "75.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "81.320", 
   "id": "s000026", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wie das Verh\u00e4ltnis der jeweiligen Minderheit zur Mehrheit ist. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "81.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "83.560", 
   "id": "s000027", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Der Bericht beschreibt sehr treffend, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "83.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "87.000", 
   "id": "s000028", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wie oft Minderheiten unterdr\u00fcckt werden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "87.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "90.560", 
   "id": "s000029", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Deshalb muss uns das eben auch mahnen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "90.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "90.880", 
   "id": "s000030", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass wir helfen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "90.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "93.880", 
   "id": "s000031", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "diese Minderheitenrechte nicht nur bei uns, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "93.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "101.600", 
   "id": "s000032", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sondern nat\u00fcrlich auch in allen anderen L\u00e4ndern immer wieder zu verteidigen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "101.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "109.160", 
   "id": "s000033", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich m\u00f6chte noch einmal auf eines hinweisen: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "109.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "114.200", 
   "id": "s000034", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Allgemeine Erkl\u00e4rung der Menschenrechte sch\u00fctzt nicht einzelne Religionen,"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "114.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "117.440", 
   "id": "s000035", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sondern sie sch\u00fctzt das Individuum."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "117.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "120.520", 
   "id": "s000036", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie sch\u00fctzt jeden Einzelnen,"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "120.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "125.280", 
   "id": "s000037", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "der sich in irgendeiner Gruppe bewegt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "125.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "127.400", 
   "id": "s000038", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "f\u00fcr sich zu entscheiden, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "127.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "130.160", 
   "id": "s000039", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ob er zu einer Religionsgemeinschaft geh\u00f6ren m\u00f6chte, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "130.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "135.360", 
   "id": "s000040", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "zu welcher er geh\u00f6ren m\u00f6chte oder ob er zu gar keiner Religionsgemeinschaft geh\u00f6ren m\u00f6chte."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "135.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "138.560", 
   "id": "s000041", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Herr Gr\u00fcbel, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "138.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "141.560", 
   "id": "s000042", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ich m\u00f6chte Ihnen gratulieren und sagen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "141.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "143.520", 
   "id": "s000043", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass ich mir sicher bin, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "143.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "146.160", 
   "id": "s000044", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass Sie Ihre Sache gut machen werden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "146.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "149.080", 
   "id": "s000045", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Aber ich m\u00f6chte noch einen Punkt im Besonderen hervorheben, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "149.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "150.640", 
   "id": "s000046", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "von dem ich glaube, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "150.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "153.560", 
   "id": "s000047", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass er einen guten Ansatz, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "153.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "154.880", 
   "id": "s000048", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "auch f\u00fcr Ihre zuk\u00fcnftige Arbeit, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "154.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "155.920", 
   "id": "s000049", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "darstellt: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "155.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "157.400", 
   "id": "s000050", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "der Religionsunterricht. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "157.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "161.280", 
   "id": "s000051", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dar\u00fcber debattieren wir viel in unserem Land, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "161.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "162.880", 
   "id": "s000052", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und zwar zu Recht. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "162.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "166.720", 
   "id": "s000053", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Der Menschenrechtsausschuss der Vereinten Nationen hat sich dahin gehend ge\u00e4u\u00dfert, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "166.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "171.360", 
   "id": "s000054", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass der Unterricht an \u00f6ffentlichen Schulen neutral und objektiv sein muss. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "171.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "172.320", 
   "id": "s000055", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wie ist das bei uns? "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "172.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "176.680", 
   "id": "s000056", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir haben in 16\u00a0Bundesl\u00e4ndern sehr unterschiedliche Modelle. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "176.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "178.800", 
   "id": "s000057", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es macht daher grunds\u00e4tzlich Sinn, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "178.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "181.240", 
   "id": "s000058", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "immer wieder deutlich zu machen: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "181.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "185.840", 
   "id": "s000059", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Bei uns ist das Recht der Religionsgemeinschaften auf einen eigenen Unterricht gesch\u00fctzt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "185.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "189.400", 
   "id": "s000060", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Manche Bundesl\u00e4nder gehen noch weiter und sagen: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "189.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "194.760", 
   "id": "s000061", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "In der Schule sollten Kinder und Jugendliche eigentlich gerade lernen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "194.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "196.800", 
   "id": "s000062", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass Menschen unterschiedlich sind, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "196.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "199.120", 
   "id": "s000063", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass sie an unterschiedliche Dinge glauben, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "199.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "205.760", 
   "id": "s000064", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass man auch bei v\u00f6llig unterschiedlicher Weltanschauung friedlich und gut zusammenleben kann. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "205.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "210.320", 
   "id": "s000065", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das machen wir beispielsweise in Hamburg mit dem Religionsunterricht f\u00fcr alle. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "210.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "211.440", 
   "id": "s000066", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich w\u00fcrde mir w\u00fcnschen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "211.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "213.840", 
   "id": "s000067", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass wir \u00fcber das Thema Religionsunterricht nicht nur, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "213.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "215.440", 
   "id": "s000068", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wenn es um andere L\u00e4nder geht, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "215.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "215.680", 
   "id": "s000069", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sondern auch, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "215.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "217.160", 
   "id": "s000070", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wenn es um die Situation bei uns geht, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "217.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "221.560", 
   "id": "s000071", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "noch viel st\u00e4rker debattieren."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "221.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "225.440", 
   "id": "s000072", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir reden heute \u00fcber allt\u00e4gliche Aggression gegen\u00fcber religi\u00f6sen Menschen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "225.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "227.160", 
   "id": "s000073", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Da kann es nur einen Schluss geben\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "227.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "227.920", 
   "id": "s000074", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ich hoffe, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "227.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "231.280", 
   "id": "s000075", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass das auch zu einem Schulterschluss f\u00fchrt\u00a0\u2013: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "231.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "234.040", 
   "id": "s000076", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Kein j\u00fcdisches Kind, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "234.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "235.440", 
   "id": "s000077", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "kein christliches Kind, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "235.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "241.960", 
   "id": "s000078", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "kein muslimisches Kind darf sich in der Schule oder auf der Stra\u00dfe unsicher f\u00fchlen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "241.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "245.200", 
   "id": "s000079", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wenn einem Jungen die Kippa vom Kopf gerissen wird, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "245.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "247.200", 
   "id": "s000080", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "m\u00fcssen wir alle vor ihm stehen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "247.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "248.080", 
   "id": "s000081", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "aber auch dann, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "248.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "252.000", 
   "id": "s000082", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wenn einem syrischen M\u00e4dchen das Kopftuch vom Kopf gerissen wird, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "252.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "255.120", 
   "id": "s000083", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "m\u00fcssen wir alle vor ihr stehen und ihr die Angst nehmen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "255.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "256.360", 
   "id": "s000084", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Vielen Dank."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "256.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "264.680", 
   "id": "s000085", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Jetzt erteile ich das Wort der Kollegin Verena Hartmann, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "264.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "265.520", 
   "id": "s000086", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "AfD, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "265.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "268.960", 
   "id": "s000087", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "zu ihrer ersten Rede im Deutschen Bundestag."
   ]
  }
 ]
}